title: fanoutqa: What are the production costs (in millions) of the top 5 highest-grossing films? (53baafef8ee1d7ff)

chat_history.content: What are the production costs (in millions) of the top 5 highest-grossing films?

Here are the top 5 highest-grossing films with their estimated production costs:

1. Avatar (2009) - Production Cost: $237 million
2. Avengers: Endgame (2019) - Production Cost: $356 million
3. Avatar: The Way of Water (2022) - Production Cost: $250 million
4. Titanic (1997) - Production Cost: $200 million
5. Star Wars: The Force Awakens (2015) - Production Cost: $245 million

These figures are in millions of dollars and are based on various online sources. Production costs can vary based on different reports and may include additional expenses beyond the initial budget.

functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.
